page.title: 06Childrens Clubs by Karen.
page.content: We did a survey of the Upper Juniors to find out what clubs and organisations the children belong to. These are the results:_ {Church Choir:}7 children {Lostwithiel Community Club:}4 children {Brownies:}3 children {Majorettes:}3 children {Scouts:}2 children {Pool Club:}2 children {Guides:}2 children {Choir(School):}2 children {Snooker Club:}1 child {Dobwalls Youth Club:}1 child {St.Pinnock Band:}1 child {Dancing Class:}1 child {Girls Brigade:}1 child {Gymnastics Club:}1 child {Swimming:}1 child
